  "title": "Small Datasets not working?",
  "body": "I found some more serious, breaking issues with the slider in V2. \r\n\r\nTo demonstrate them I wanted to create a small subset but this only works with the search box but not the refinement list or more than one slider. \r\n\r\nTaking the full dataset (6000+ entries) is no problem besides the problems with the slider. \r\n\r\nSo is there a minimum number of data points that instantsearch needs to work?\r\n\r\nhttps://jsfiddle.net/bjav561j/\r\n\r\nThis is the dataset used:\r\n\r\n```json\r\n[\r\n{\r\n  \"name\": \"Sandra\",\r\n  \"year_of_birth\": 1993, \r\n  \"hair_color\": \"Blond\",\r\n  \"height\": 1, \r\n  \"objectID\": \"Sandra\"\r\n},\r\n{\r\n  \"name\": \"Michael\",\r\n  \"year_of_birth\": 1960, \r\n  \"hair_color\": \"Brown\",\r\n  \"height\": 2, \r\n  \"objectID\": \"Michael\"\r\n},\r\n{\r\n  \"name\": \"Petra\",\r\n  \"year_of_birth\": 1985, \r\n  \"hair_color\": \"Black\",\r\n  \"height\": 3, \r\n  \"objectID\": \"Petra\"\r\n},\r\n{\r\n  \"name\": \"Jim\",\r\n  \"year_of_birth\": 1975, \r\n  \"hair_color\": \"Brown\",\r\n  \"height\": 4, \r\n  \"objectID\": \"Jim\"\r\n},\r\n{\r\n  \"name\": \"Marc\",\r\n  \"year_of_birth\": 1987, \r\n  \"hair_color\": \"Blond\",\r\n  \"height\": 5, \r\n  \"objectID\": \"Marc\"\r\n},\r\n{\r\n  \"name\": \"John\",\r\n  \"year_of_birth\": 1960, \r\n  \"hair_color\": \"Black\",\r\n  \"height\": 6, \r\n  \"objectID\": \"Sandra\"\r\n},\r\n{\r\n  \"name\": \"Kelly\",\r\n  \"year_of_birth\": 1998, \r\n  \"hair_color\": \"Black\",\r\n  \"height\": 7, \r\n  \"objectID\": \"Kelly\"\r\n},\r\n{\r\n  \"name\": \"Adriana\",\r\n  \"year_of_birth\": 1990, \r\n  \"hair_color\": \"Brown\",\r\n  \"height\": 8, \r\n  \"objectID\": \"Adriana\"\r\n},\r\n{\r\n  \"name\": \"Jennifer\",\r\n  \"year_of_birth\": 1978, \r\n  \"hair_color\": \"Blond\",\r\n  \"height\": 9, \r\n  \"objectID\": \"Jennifer\"\r\n},\r\n{\r\n  \"name\": \"Sarah\",\r\n  \"year_of_birth\": 1988, \r\n  \"hair_color\": \"Blonde\",\r\n  \"height\": 10, \r\n  \"objectID\": \"Sarah\"\r\n},\r\n{\r\n  \"name\": \"Otto\",\r\n  \"year_of_birth\": 1999, \r\n  \"hair_color\": \"Red\",\r\n  \"height\": 11, \r\n  \"objectID\": \"Otto\"\r\n},\r\n{\r\n  \"name\": \"Paul\",\r\n  \"year_of_birth\": 1986, \r\n  \"hair_color\": \"Brown\",\r\n  \"height\": 12, \r\n  \"objectID\": \"Paul\"\r\n}]\r\n```",
